title: Neff in the Parks | Superpark 2015
description: Superpark 19 is in the books! A few hundred of the best snowboarders in the world all met up for the 19th annual Superpark session in Seven Springs, Pennsylvania to showcase their skills on some absolutely massive features. A few Neff Team members joined the world's best and put together this edit for your viewing pleasure. Watch Tim Humphreys, Chas Guldemond, Taylor Gold, Brandon Davis, Matt Williams and friends go huge. Big thanks to Wojciech Targosz, editing/filming master. See photo highlights: https://www.neffheadwear.com/blog/nef...
